## Do this exact change

Use this exact code, with the constant at class level:

```java
private static final Pattern DATE_PATTERN =
        Pattern.compile("(\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}|\\d{12}|\\d{8})");

private Optional<LocalDate> extractDateFromFileName(String fileName) {
    Matcher matcher = DATE_PATTERN.matcher(fileName);

    if (!matcher.find()) {
        return Optional.empty();
    }

    String dateStr = matcher.group();

    try {
        if (dateStr.length() == 10) {
            return Optional.of(LocalDate.parse(dateStr));
        }

        if (dateStr.length() == 12) {
            return Optional.of(
                    LocalDate.parse(dateStr.substring(0, 8), DateTimeFormatter.BASIC_ISO_DATE)
            );
        }

        if (dateStr.length() == 8) {
            return Optional.of(LocalDate.parse(dateStr, DateTimeFormatter.BASIC_ISO_DATE));
        }
    } catch (Exception e) {
        return Optional.empty();
    }

    return Optional.empty();
}
```

